g.title: QY
g.text: Is the master connected to the system's outputs?

g.title: AYN
g.text: Connect the master to the system's outputs

g.title: QYY
g.text: Do sound work when Ardour is OFF?

g.title: QYYYL
g.text: What sound system am I using?

g.title: QYYYLJ
g.text: When starting jack, do I have an error 'jack server is not running or cannot be started'?

g.title: QYYYLJY
g.text: When starting Jack, do I have an error 'Cannot lock down memory'?

g.title: AYYYLJYY
g.text: If it is named /etc/security/limits.d/audio.conf.disabled, rename it to the former.
Then log out and log in again

g.title: QNY
g.text: Is there any audio/MIDI in the session?

g.title: QNNN
g.text: In Window > Audio/MIDI setup, is the Audio system stopped?

g.title: QNYY
g.text: In the mixer, is any track meter moving?

g.title: QNYYY
g.text: Is this track connected to Master?

g.title: QNYYN
g.text: Is a track having audio content rec-enabled?

g.title: ANYYYN
g.text: Connect the track output to Master

g.title: QNYYYYNN
g.text: Is the gain slider for this track grayed?

g.title: ANYYYYNNN
g.text: Increase the gain on this track

g.title: QNYYNNY
g.text: Is there any plugin on this track?

g.title: ANYYNNYY
g.text: Disable all the plugins on this track
